&lt;div class=&quot;&quot; data-automation-id=&quot;job-description&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Scope&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a senior radio software engineer at Ambiq, you will drive wireless software development for the Apollo Blue family and develop wireless software solutions (implement specifications, design software, and unit test). This role will work with different cross-functional teams to integrate and debug wireless components on the company’s platform. Perform code review, code optimization, refactoring, bug hunting, and bug fixing.&lt;/p&gt;
