&lt;li&gt;Produce unit, functional, integration, and interoperability tests, including automating tests when advantageous.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work with Product Planning Team to understand system requirements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work with validation and system test teams to triage issues and communicate their status to management.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
